ass=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maxito3/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/129c38ff58ae6af20bd5894ba36ad5b5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/129c38ff58ae6af20bd5894ba36ad5b5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maxito3/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">maxito3</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">abril 8, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It works, simple to use but very effective.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin! Simple yet functional and beautiful.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/passiondigitalpublishing/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1ad72a9801e4a5f631805ac863a11df?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1ad72a9801e4a5f631805ac863a11df?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/passiondigitalpublishing/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Passion <small>(PassionDigitalPublishing)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">abril 5, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is so simple to set up and use and provides beautiful templates and flexibility to customise.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does what it&#039;s supposed to do</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/xampit/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/adbb77bacb58b53ff1e420ae0a7f73d1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/adbb77bacb58b53ff1e420ae0a7f73d1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/xampit/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">xampit</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">marzo 29, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Does what it\'s supposed to do and that quite well.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works good, Looks good!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/russellv/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3a8442434e99c0619c73135865393f80?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3a8442434e99c0619c73135865393f80?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/russellv/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">russellv</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">marzo 22, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin makes the login easy. Design the login page any way you want it. The quality is excellent. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excelent, Work great!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\">